OL,3,CHollywood royalty Jeff Goldblum pays a
OL,4,Cvisit to Brighton
OL,6,FWatch: Hollywood's Jeff Goldblum
OL,7,Fdances with fans at a Brighton record
OL,8,Fstore
OL,10,FActor Jeff Goldblum thrilled more than
OL,11,F500 fans when he dropped in at a
OL,12,Frecord store in Brighton on Friday.
OL,14,FHe visited Resident Music in the city
OL,15,Fto launch his new album 'Night Blooms'.
OL,17,FThe star of Jurassic Park and The Fly
OL,18,Fis an avid jazz fan and plays piano.
OL,20,FFans queued to meet the A-lister and
OL,21,Fsome had the change to dance with him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
