PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781082348
OL,3,CHollywood royalty Jeff Goldblum pays a
OL,4,Cvisit to Brighton
OL,6,FGoldblum told fans that is was his
OL,7,Ffirst time visiting the city and said
OL,8,Fto one that he "might move here".
OL,10,FWhen the A-lister wasn't speaking to
OL,11,Ffans, he was asking staff for their
OL,12,Frecommendations of records to get.
OL,14,FStaff at the record store said they
OL,15,Fwere pinching themselves over the
OL,16,Factors visit.
OL,18,FGoldblum's new album, 'Night Blooms'
OL,19,Fis a companion to his 2025 record
OL,20,F'Still Blooming'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
