OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1781082348
OL,3,CHollywood royalty Jeff Goldblum pays a
OL,4,Cvisit to Brighton
OL,6,FIt features his long time band The
OL,7,FMildred Snitzer Orchestra.
OL,9,FJeff Goldblum's career spans almost
OL,10,Fsix decades of award winning work in
OL,11,Ffilm, television and theatre.
OL,13,FAs well as acting, he is an Oscar
OL,14,Fnominated director for his short
OL,15,Ffeature film "Little Surprises".
OL,17,FRecently, he co-starred as 'The Wizard
OL,18,Fof Oz', in Wicked with Ariana Grande
OL,19,Fand Cynthia Erivo.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
